{"tid":509012,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[全方位］國家打吡兩部專機影實C朗美斯","createTime":"2017-12-24T20:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T15:46:19.000Z","uid":119350,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"13a10a001c5c1c64ee8b069c7ef5649e41e7671d","tid":509012,"uid":119350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T20:56:09.000Z","msg":"國家打吡兩部專機影實C朗美斯<br />\n<br />\n兩部攝錄機將在在90分鐘內跟實基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）和美斯（Lionel Messi），西甲方面發出聲明說，「兩部攝錄機將分別全程捕捉葡萄牙前鋒和阿根廷隊前鋒，讓球迷們可以<span style=\"color: red;\"> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大飽眼福</span></span>，欣賞兩位巨星的每一個舉動。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，有關方面亦有兩個鏡頭專門捕捉兩隊教練施丹和華維迪的舉動，「同樣的情況也適用於教練席的兩位主帥，由第一個哨子聲開始就會捕捉施丹和華維迪。」<br />\n<br />\n「為了讓電視觀眾感受置身看台一樣，班拿貝球場還將配備一個虛擬的「Be The Player」相機，該相機採用了<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 360度技術</span></span>，是西甲廣播的第一次。這個攝錄機會從球員角度出發，為觀眾提供和他們的英雄一樣的視角。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 原來咁樣用嘅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/dysXev.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FdysXev.gif&h=e6a4afca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fac4b25fd0b2a40d491428ca03eacc1c57e8cbf7","tid":509012,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T23:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749cd136a05d326d32102919616d85af2d5c396a","tid":509012,"uid":16567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T00:09:47.000Z","msg":"撻Q360<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d914ed0b4435b4ff132ea3289d119a1d76a507c5","tid":509012,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"